QuestData.Title: Thumping Knucklethump
QuestData.Description: The Knucklethump hozen have new chief, the Ook of Dook.$b$bHe sees fear in the west, anger in the south, hatred in the north, and yaungols in the east.$b$bAnd so he sets his hozen to ravage, gathering food and supplies for coming famine.$b$bThey are many Knucklethumps and dangerous.$b$bPlease, Luckydo, can you defeat their fighters?
QuestData.LogDescription: Slay 8 Knucklethump Smashers or Jibstabbers at Knucklethump Hole.
